":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I'd like to wear slippers when I'm at home. （我在家喜欢穿拖"},{"type":"text","text":"鞋。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Same here. （我也是。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Time for you to go to bed. （你该睡觉了。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Really? I didn't realize it was so late. （是吗？我没意识到已经"},{"type":"text","text":"这么晚了。）"}]}]}